ZH: 生物是指能够独立存在、呼吸、摄取营养并能进行繁殖的有机体。
EN: Organisms are living entities that can live independently, breathe, obtain nutrition, and reproduce.
ZH: 多细胞生物是由多个细胞组成的生物。
EN: Multicellular organisms are organisms composed of multiple cells.
ZH: 生物多样性是地球上各种生物种类丰富而独特的特征。
EN: Biodiversity refers to the richness and uniqueness of the various species on Earth.
ZH: 植物和动物都是地球上最常见的生物。
EN: Plants and animals are the most common organisms on Earth.
ZH: 微生物是一类极小的生物，例如细菌和病毒。
EN: Microorganisms are a class of extremely small organisms, such as bacteria and viruses.
ZH: 生物学是研究生物的科学学科。
EN: Biology is the scientific discipline that studies organisms.
ZH: 鸟类是一类有羽毛、会飞翔的生物。
EN: Birds are a class of organisms that have feathers and can fly.
ZH: 人类属于哺乳动物这一类生物。
EN: Humans belong to the category of mammals in the animal kingdom.
ZH: 自然界有许多奇特的生物形态，如僵尸蟑螂海参和食人植物。
EN: The natural world is full of unique organism morphologies, such as zombie cockroaches, sea cucumbers, and carnivorous plants.
ZH: 生物对环境的适应能力是它们能够在不同生态系统中生存的关键。
EN: The ability of organisms to adapt to their environment is crucial for their survival in different ecosystems.
ZH: 生物的生命周期包括出生、成长、繁殖和死亡。
EN: The life cycle of organisms includes birth, growth, reproduction, and death.
ZH: 生物进化是生命多样性形成和演化的过程。
EN: Biological evolution is the process of the formation and evolution of life diversity.
ZH: 大熊猫是中国的国宝，也是濒临灭绝的生物之一。
EN: Giant pandas are a national treasure of China and one of the endangered species.
ZH: 生物能源是以生物质为原料生产能源的一种方式。
EN: Bioenergy is a way of producing energy using biomass as raw material.
ZH: 生物工程是利用生物技术来改造和利用生物的工程学科。
EN: Biotechnology is an engineering discipline that uses biological technology to modify and utilize organisms.
ZH: 遗传学研究了生物遗传信息传递和遗传性状的变化。
EN: Genetics studies the transmission of genetic information and the variation of inherited traits in organisms.
ZH: 生物学家使用显微镜来观察微小的生物结构和细胞。
EN: Biologists use microscopes to observe tiny biological structures and cells.
ZH: 生物技术的发展为制药、农业等领域带来了巨大的创新。
EN: The development of biotechnology has brought great innovations to fields such as pharmaceuticals and agriculture.
ZH: 环境保护是为了维护生物多样性和生态平衡。
EN: Environmental protection aims to preserve biodiversity and ecological balance.
